item.title: CVE-2023-5604|2023-11-27T16:22:00.940Z -- unknown -- asgaros%20forum
item.description: The Asgaros Forum WordPress plugin before 2.7.1 allows forum administrators, who may not be WordPress (super-)administrators, to set insecure configuration that allows unauthenticated users to upload dangerous files (e.g. .php, .phtml), potentially leading to remote code execution.
